649. J Neurosurg. 2009 Nov;111(5):970-7. doi: 10.3171/2009.4.JNS08568.

Benefit of carotid endarterectomy for symptomatic and asymptomatic severe 
carotid artery stenosis: a Markov model based on data from randomized controlled 
